highlights.text: Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Ahmedabad. Kesariya is the highest at #1.
Heer Ranjha by Rito Riba, Rajat Nagpal, and Rana Sotal is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Ahmedabad, up 63 spots at #10.
Tu Aake Dekhle by King has been on Top Songs Ahmedabad the longest, at 56 weeks straight.
Kho Gaye by Taaruk Raina and Mismatched - Cast is the highest new entry on Top Songs Ahmedabad at #32.
